title: GODZILLA - RULERS OF EARTH 001 (2013) (Digital) (TLK-Empire-HD)
description:
Godzilla: Rulers of Earth #1

Story by Chris Mowry, Matt Frank
Art by Matt Frank
Colors by Ronda Pattison
Letters by Shawn Lee

Publisher: IDW
Release Date: June 26th, 2013

In the wake of the climactic conclusion of Godzilla #13 comes a brand new series! Dozens of new monsters have risen from the depth and are staking out their own territory, regardless of humanity's political borders! A war of dominance begins... will Godzilla end up on top? First he'll have to beat a new upstart... Zilla!
